# Large binary assets — tracked via Git LFS (see .gitattributes).
# Do NOT gitignore these patterns: LFS stores the pointer in git and
# the blob out-of-band. Ignoring them would break the tracking.
#   *.fbx  *.uasset  *.umap  *.wav  *.exr  *.hdr  *.mp4

